'''椅子樂團'''（英文團名：The Chairs）<ref>{{cite web |title=Hard Riff現場實錄：少年椅子樂團的熟成老靈魂 |url=https://www.redbull.com/tw-zh/hardriff-chairs-show-interview |website=Red Bull |access-date=2020-10-30 |archive-date=2020-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101175343/https://www.redbull.com/tw-zh/hardriff-chairs-show-interview |dead-url=no }}</ref>，台灣三人編制樂團。由主唱兼吉他手詠靖、主唱兼吉他手仲穎以及貝斯手伯元組成。2019年以第二張專輯《Lovely Sunday樂芙莉聖代》<ref>{{cite web |title=椅子樂團如何透過《樂芙莉聖代》重振旗鼓，抖落厭世塵埃？ |url=https://blow.streetvoice.com/41950 |website=吹音樂 |access-date=2020-10-30 |archive-date=2021-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119030904/https://blow.streetvoice.com/41950/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>榮獲第三十屆金曲獎「最佳演唱組合」。<ref>{{cite web |title=金曲獎／椅子樂團奪最佳演唱組合！　一上台嗨炸：Wow 原文網址: 金曲獎／椅子樂團奪最佳演唱組合！　一上台嗨炸：Wow |url=https://star.ettoday.net/news/1478420 |website=ETtoday星光雲 |access-date=2020-10-30 |archive-date=2020-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102123857/https://star.ettoday.net/news/1478420 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

